@startuml seq-checkout-webhook
skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam noteBorderColor #999
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFFDE7

title LemonSqueezy Checkout URL & Webhook Verification

actor "Consumer App" as App
participant "LicenseGate" as Gate
participant "LemonSqueezyCheckout" as LSC
participant "LemonSqueezyWebhook" as LSW
participant "LemonSqueezy\nStorefront" as LS

== Build checkout URL (after a Denied result) ==

App -> Gate : checkoutUrl(email, variantId)
Gate -> LSC : buildCheckoutUrl(email, variantId, null)
LSC -> LSC : URL-encode params\nhttps://{store}.lemonsqueezy.com/buy/{variantId}?checkout[email]=...
LSC --> Gate : URI
Gate --> App : URI

App -> LS : redirect user to checkout URI
note right of LS : User completes purchase\nin LemonSqueezy hosted checkout

== Webhook verification (in consumer's HTTP server) ==

LS -> App : POST /webhook\n  X-Signature: <hex>\n  body: <raw JSON>

App -> LSW : verifySignature(rawBody, header, signingSecret)
LSW -> LSW : HMAC-SHA256(rawBody, secret)\nconstant-time compare
LSW --> App : true / false

alt signature valid
  App -> App : parse body, activate license\n(call Keygen to create/activate license key)
else signature invalid
  App --> LS : 401 Unauthorized
end

@enduml
